               <p>JOHN LAMER. On the day in the indictment, the shop bell was rung violently, and on going down stairs, I perceived there was nobody in the shop,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181604030062"></xptr>and I understood from the people round the door, that my young man had gone in quest of some body who had stolen something.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160403-130-person993">
